{
  "script_id": "latin-square",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "latin-square",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/latin-square/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "你一定玩过数独，在九宫格里让数字不重复。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "latin-square",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/latin-square/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "其实数独有一位更古老的祖先，叫做拉丁方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "latin-square",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/latin-square/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "早在两百多年前，数学家欧拉就深入研究过它。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "latin-square",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "define-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/latin-square/yunxi/define-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "一个 n 阶拉丁方，是用 n 个符号填满的 n 乘 n 方阵。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "latin-square",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "define-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/latin-square/yunxi/define-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "要求每一行都用到全部符号，每一列也用到全部符号。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "latin-square",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "define-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/latin-square/yunxi/define-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "也就是说，同一行、同一列里绝不出现重复。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "latin-square",
      "section_id": "construct",
      "line_id": "con-1",
      "filename": "construct-con-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/latin-square/yunxi/construct-con-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.54,
      "size": 40608,
      "text": "最简单的造法是循环移位：每往下一行，就把符号整体右移一格。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "latin-square",
      "section_id": "construct",
      "line_id": "con-2",
      "filename": "construct-con-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/latin-square/yunxi/construct-con-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "用公式说，第 i 行第 j 列填 i 加 j 对 n 取余。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "latin-square",
      "section_id": "construct",
      "line_id": "con-3",
      "filename": "construct-con-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/latin-square/yunxi/construct-con-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "取余保证了符号在每行每列都恰好轮一遍，绝不撞车。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "latin-square",
      "section_id": "orthogonal",
      "line_id": "ort-1",
      "filename": "orthogonal-ort-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/latin-square/yunxi/orthogonal-ort-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38160,
      "text": "把两个拉丁方叠在一起，如果所有符号对都不重复，就称它们正交。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "latin-square",
      "section_id": "orthogonal",
      "line_id": "ort-2",
      "filename": "orthogonal-ort-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/latin-square/yunxi/orthogonal-ort-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.54,
      "size": 40608,
      "text": "正交拉丁方是农业和工业实验设计的利器，能均衡地消除行列干扰。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "latin-square",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/latin-square/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "调整阶数，看拉丁方如何从小方阵长成大棋盘。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "latin-square",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/latin-square/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "换一种循环移位，观察校验器告诉你它是否仍然合法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "latin-square",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/latin-square/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "拉丁方要求每行每列都不重复，是数独的数学骨架。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "latin-square",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/latin-square/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "循环移位轻松构造，正交结构支撑起实验设计。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "latin-square",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/latin-square/yunxi/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "小小方阵里藏着大大的组合智慧，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
